# Exception: backlog task description files (.md) may legitimately contain
# ".bak" in their title (e.g. TASK-30). Keep them tracked. Real *.bak backups
# do not end in .md, so they remain ignored. (TASK-85 filename-hygiene family.)
!backlog/tasks/*.md
